</title>
<subSubSection id="9225D6B3BEDF8B26E1E81F5438DE50B0" pageId="null" pageNumber="827" type="description">
<paragraph id="7A5BF110246E5226964B505803A967FB" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">
Ausdauernd, lockerrasig; 5-15 cm hoch. Stengel aufsteigend, verzweigt, kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="8C7DD29A9D965D52428FECFA064698C2" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
undeutlich 1nervig, fleischig (etwa 1 mm dick, aber oben flach), schmal lanzettlich, 0,5-1,5 cm lang, 
<emphasis id="608603B4674ADF29E3D12AECAE438510" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">4-8mal so lang wie breit</emphasis>
, kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="40565DB591A36EAF5C88DA18D0762C6A" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Blueten</normalizedToken>
zu 1-3 am Ende der Zweige. 
<normalizedToken id="DE6C4ACD3DAD767361B7CFD9ABF96DDB" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
4-8mal so lang wie die kleinen, 
<normalizedToken id="EDFBD058A18BC87FF6FFAFA8644B5787" originalValue="häutig" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">haeutig</normalizedToken>
berandeten obersten 
<normalizedToken id="2339113D4CE8E2A8451AB704D241D47E" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="561B4832ACE9AAEDBD916885247C0989" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
5, lanzettlich, spitz, 3-4 mm lang, mit im untern Teil 0,2-0,4 mm breitem 
<normalizedToken id="DCE99418BC24EFD74DADB07449AA3A0B" originalValue="häutigem" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">haeutigem</normalizedToken>
Rand, 1nervig, kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="B74552CB2051C511D9FF635487C85E45" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
5, etwa 
<normalizedToken id="CDA330F9B4ABE8A15AEDC52DF513AC98" originalValue="1½" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">11/2</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="5C5287FBA546B97CBA291E91C07D3784" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="9C7A1CBFCCC6EC65000F42A958BA6A91" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">weiss</normalizedToken>
. Kapsel ⅔-⅘ so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="E0CAD52EFB41184377314FBD8A4CA058" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="A6AC83AF2A34676F2BA3E2029E1A4454" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">
Samen 1,5-1,8 mm lang, mit 
<normalizedToken id="90397AA066D4379392D266B45B75F33C" originalValue="groβem" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">groβem</normalizedToken>
, ganzrandigem 
<normalizedToken id="D64F33FA692E362C37E43BB291A2D50A" originalValue="Anhängsel" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Anhaengsel</normalizedToken>
. -
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="8575FB6D63D593C2FFF6CE267644FBED" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C37533A595093C61F8C2F8FFB73DEBC9" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">
<emphasis id="6EDD819187AA9FF0AB707A3097E78E0F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="A4C5E2D6BF5E796A9C9F7409D2B1BDFA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">24:</emphasis>
Material von der Presolana (Favarger 1965).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1C8F76C5C0A1301FF9F8961D41904993" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">
<emphasis id="D4848B8402D3E27374C1B77D80C9BBFE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan (1300-1400 m). Schattige Kalkfelsen (nach Mattfeld 1925 mit 
<emphasis id="3D8353415F5AE5D3F054624DD8F685E5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">
<taxonomicName id="EF157F90FE728BC2FA700EEABE64211F" authority="Bonarota" authorityName="Bonarota" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Veronica" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="827" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Veronica Bonarota</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="F0AEE366974E483FFAB493381D1F9CD4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Campanula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="827" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="elatinoides">Campanula elatinoides</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="CFED263A1694E9F9A5D598BB7A4597BD" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Potentilla" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="null" pageNumber="827" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="caulescens">Potentilla caulescens</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="0F0D8546636370E88848C29FAC830E4A" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Silene" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="827" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Silene</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName id="F1F999FE086234676B848AD58EC58AC4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Saxifragaceae" genus="Saxifraga" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="null" pageNumber="827" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Saxifraga</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="53A01F17FB9575D4F004C3D9998635BF" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">
<emphasis id="F87BB7D99CE73153F5BB1AD9C04FFD65" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="827">Verbreitung. Bergamasker Pflanze:</emphasis>
Presolana.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
